{"tid":1448441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:01.000Z","uid":127426,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12678e55f39932ea7f0938b0f9c3472f1bd9b461","tid":1448441,"uid":127426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=7c1307b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n<br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=a728eaff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"36afdfe4a8b0ce211e73908594db4e5863771f5a","tid":1448441,"uid":75391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:41.000Z","msg":"毋忘 721 811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 元朗、荃灣、北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 太古車站推人落電梯，近距離行刑式掃射<br />\n5. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n6. 製造偽証，插贓嫁禍"},{"pid":"8788decc735350c0cb01dd05c7dd01e6c1ae2628","tid":1448441,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:52.000Z","msg":"721 811 解散警隊"},{"pid":"b970b9c8f4e0599c3b78597c8aad6bdec9dccb55","tid":1448441,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0814b28c5216203b99a9365961e206000779c42d","tid":1448441,"uid":122676,"like